text: Daoura is a small town and rural commune in Tarfaya Province of the Laâyoune- Sakia El Hamra region of Morocco. At the time of the 2014 census, the commune had a total population of 1108 people. ==References== Category:Populated places in Laâyoune-Sakia El Hamra Category:Tarfaya
title: Daoura
